curam.util.ieg.impl
Class IEGScriptResult

java.lang.Object
  curam.util.ieg.impl.IEGScriptResult

public class IEGScriptResult
extends java.lang.Object

The IEGScriptResult class represents a summary of an IEGScriptExecution excluding textual elements. A script result contains page results for all the question pages displayed in a tree structure.
